TY  - GEN
TI  - Exploring the Relationship Between Instagram Use and Body Image Issues Among Teenagers
AU  - Vidyawati Vidyawati
PY  - 2024
UR  - https://gensain.com/index.php/mjds/article/download/43/35
DO  - 10.37899/mjds.v1i2.43
JO  - Mahogany Journal De Social
AB  - Experimental online study (N = 226) exposing participants to either idealized body images or body-diversity images on Instagram. The idealized content group showed increased body dissatisfaction; the diversity group showed improvement. Upward social comparison tendency and internalization of beauty ideals moderated the effects. **Methodology:** Online randomized experiment; mixed ANOVA with repeated measures. **Limitations:** Mostly female sample; body dissatisfaction proxied for anxiety; no long-term follow-up.
